%N A029898 Pitoun's sequence: a(n+1) is digital root of a(0) + ... + a(n).
%C A029898 If the initial 1 is omitted, this is 2^n mod 9. - _N. J. A. Sloane_
%C A029898 From _Cino Hilliard_, Dec 31 2004: (Start)
